:1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:04:24.000Z","msg":"太子站一定唔會炒車<br />\n至少有五個情況嚴重 (HA話嘅)<br />\n所以警方一定有用致命武力<br />\n<br />\n記者一定要問清楚<br />\n1. [HA]醫管局所指嘅「831公眾活動」包唔包太子月台黑警無差別襲擊<br />\n2. [HA]啲人點傷 有無骨折有無內出血有無腦部受傷有無癱<br />\n3. [Popo]送院無人死亡，但現場有無？<br />\n4. [Popo/MTR]邊個導致嗰五個情況嚴重 係popo定乘客 點解無即時送院 要送去荔枝角站先嘅<br />\n5. [MTR]有無嗰五個情況嚴重嘅CCTV 有無俾家屬睇<br />\n6. [MTR]五名乘客喺太子站警察執法後嚴重受傷 點保障乘客安全 有無考慮投訴監警會<br />\n<br />\n另外唔好share圖<br />\n啲狗想用假消息狼來了掩飾真相<br />\n所以我哋一定要製造輿論到有CCTV為止"},{"pid":"550d281fded110d2447b68a2084a3d7c17b4da1b","tid":1533061,"uid":234402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd5d8897ca2d05c333439578391680006c212aac","tid":1533061,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:50:07.000Z","msg":"我嘅話 就真係打機打到認真mode 部機放係屎眼入面震都sense唔到"},{"pid":"0e0b5199cf080635dbb1f4a80ece3efa5a9affb0","tid":1533061,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:50:37.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<b